<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
	<title>Application Status Update</title>
	<style>
		body {
			background-color: #f7f7f7;
			padding: 20px;
			font-family: ui-sans-serif;
			margin: 0;
		}

		.email-container {
			max-width: 800px;
			margin: auto;
			background: white;
			border-radius: 5px;
			overflow: hidden;
			border: 1px solid rgb(40, 53, 147);
			border-radius: 10px;
		}

		.header {
			background-color: rgb(40, 53, 147);
			text-align: center;
			border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
			padding: 10px;
		}

		.logo {
			max-height: 120px;
		}

		.email-content {
			padding: 30px;
		}

		.email-content h2 {
			text-align: center;
		}

		.status-box {
			background-color: #f0f4fb;
			padding: 15px 20px;
			border-radius: 8px;
			margin: 20px 0;
			line-height: 1.6;
			font-size: 16px;
		}

		.status-approved {
			color: green;
			font-weight: bold;
		}

		.status-rejected {
			color: red;
			font-weight: bold;
		}

		.footer {
			padding: 20px;
			background: rgb(40, 53, 147);
			text-align: center;
			font-size: 12px;
			color: #FFF;
			border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
		}

		.footer p {
			margin: 5px 0;
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="email-container">
		<div class="header">
			<img src="cid:logo" alt="QuarterTracker Logo" class="logo" />
		</div>
		<div class="email-content" style="color: black!important">
			<h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>
			<p>We wanted to inform you that the status of your quarter application has been updated.</p>

			<div class="status-box">
				<strong>Application Status:</strong>
				<span class="<%= status === 'Approved' ? 'status-approved' : 'status-rejected' %>">
					<%= status %>
				</span><br/>

				<% if (status === 'Rejected') { %>
					<strong>Reason:</strong> <%= rejectReason %>
				<% } %>
			</div>

			<p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to contact the administration.</p>

			<p>Thank you!<br />Team QuarterTracker</p>
		</div>
		<div class="footer">
			<p>Copyright Â© 2025 QuarterTracker, All rights reserved.</p>
			<p>
				<strong>Our mailing address is:</strong><br />
				Sunshine Tower, 30th Floor, Senapati Bapat Marg,<br />
				Dadar West, Mumbai 400013, Maharashtra, India
			</p>
			<p><a href="#" style="color: #fff!important">Unsubscribe</a></p>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
